"tid":2315114,"uid":339272,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T06:41:12.000Z","msg":"間房幾大，第時可以做職業兒子"},{"pid":"b799f5487a974c8605243dc502061292c6b4bd2d","tid":2315114,"uid":325881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ebdc959d8cc8dbe42b795b9fa1042c5053dc54eb","tid":2315114,"uid":22108,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T05:13:03.000Z","msg":"60萬生個b+扲美籍<br />\n低啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T09:10:42.000Z","msg":"60萬現金<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71bfa8c096c7a83a660e294f1d3c9124d2140b0d","tid":2315114,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8da05c057dad4d3f0e63ae1c7b907af1b1485933","tid":2315114,"uid":8171,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T04:38:24.000Z","msg":"個小朋友自小缺乏父愛好易心理唔平衡"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T09:12:24.000Z","msg":"冇男人教小朋友人生道理 個小朋友大個咗都唔會好得去邊"},{"pid":"11f300ecb243f3f2d707e06addbc06673ae3eec5","tid":2315114,"uid":209890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T09:16:36.000Z","msg":"想屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e58cac942edc5f02c6cfd186d98cca4f427148f3","tid":2315114,"uid":282637,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T09:23:15.000Z","msg":"雖然她不乏戀愛經驗，卻沒遇上能令她付託一生的對象，<br />\n<br />\n點解一定係男問題,唔會係女嘅問題?"},{"pid":"33f0bd4d95c1b2015f3c4abcf629e7ac3e4fd0c8","tid":2315114,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T09:28:17.000Z","msg":"如果用60萬養一個後生仔一年日日鋤其實有無可能大肚?"},{"pid":"04875d9c933a48a8a9f95cd27d85e44b13684e37","tid":2315114,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T10:02:38.000Z","msg":"害左個細路"}]}